# Stray files written into the repo by tools that are not this project.
#
# MCP servers configured with a RELATIVE data path write wherever the agent's
# cwd happens to be, which is a session's worktree. `data/wowlogs-mcp.db` turned
# up in two worktrees this way — nothing to do with Starbase, but it shows up as
# untracked in every `git status` and invites being committed by accident.
#
# Anchored at the repo root, so a legitimate nested fixture dir
# (`packages/*/data/`) is still tracked.
/data/
